The proposed algorithm involves inferring a temporal model of a scene with semantic instance information, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper presents experiments with a new benchmark for the new task, which could be relevant to graphics (cs.GR).
